l-kadhib","tag-guarding-the-tongue","tag-unlawful-al-haram","tag-idolatry-shirk","tag-major-sins-al-kabair","tag-monotheism-tawhid","tag-obedience-al-taah","tag-parents-walidayn","tag-speech-al-qawl"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-LJ","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":32841,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/21\/three-worst-major-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":2959,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Kaba\u2019ir: Three of the worst major sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 21, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakrah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said three times, \u201cShall I not tell you about the worst of major sins?\u201d They said, \u201cOf course, O Messenger of Allah.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThey are to associate partners with Allah and to be disrespectful to parents.\u201d Then,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32182,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/avoid-seven-mortal-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":2959,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Sins: Avoid seven major sins, idolatry, killing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cStay away from seven mortal sins.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what are they?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cIdolatry with Allah, occult magic, killing a soul that Allah has sanctified except for a just cause, consuming usury, usurping\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5164,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/15\/innovation-bidah-in-religion\/","url_meta":{"origin":2959,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Bidah: Innovations in religion are rejected by Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever innovates into this matter of ours that which does not belong to it, it will be rejected.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2697, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1718 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7564,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/03\/major-sins-idolatry-murder\/","url_meta":{"origin":2959,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sins: Major sins are idolatry, infanticide, adultery","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas'ud reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what is the greatest sin?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTo set up a partner alongside Allah, even though He alone created you.\u201d I said, \u201cWhat is next?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cTo kill your child, fearing\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7501,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/03\/curse-own-parents\/","url_meta":{"origin":2959,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Curses: Prohibition of cursing another&#8217;s parents","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, among the major sins is that a man curses his own parents.\u201d It was said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, how can a man curse his own parents?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cHe insults the father\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2963,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/19\/dies-shirk-idolatry-ploytheism-nar\/","url_meta":{"origin":2959,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Shirk: Whoever dies associating idols with Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 19, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas'ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever dies while associating partners with Allah will enter Hellfire.\u201d And I said in his presence, \u201cWhoever dies without associating partners with Allah will enter Paradise.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1181,\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 92 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\